Maintainer: JT <jtmoree@users.noreply.github.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/jtmoree-github-com/luks-root-smartcard

Package: luks-root-smartcard-tools
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, cryptsetup-initramfs, initramfs-tools, gnupg, opensc, pcscd, systemd-cryptsetup
Description: Smartcard and TPM2-based LUKS root unlock for Debian/Ubuntu
 Provides initramfs hooks and boot scripts that unlock the root volume
 using a smartcard (pkcs11-tool or GPG/scdaemon) or a TPM2 token
 enrolled with systemd-cryptenroll.
